Product Assistant Manager - PT Sinar Meadow International Indonesia
Product Assistant Manager  -
Product Assistant Manager
Responsibilities
Manages existing products & services as well as creating and integrating new products and product changes throughout company.Conducts margin analysis, industry research, and in-life performance measurement to determine product demand, positioning, viability, and profitability.Project management of all product integration/launches/changes throughout implementation.Identify the business and operational requirements based upon the business requirements & objectives of each product.Coordinate and build strong working relations with various internal organizations and driving a solution set across development through market requirements, product contract, and positioning.Leads regularly scheduled meetings centered on system and operational requirements for product changes and new product development. Develops pricing, pricing changes and manages tariff updates internally.Pre-empts potential problems and provides effective solutions in reaction to the application of concepts, techniques, knowledge, or processes developed to support the new product or product change. Identify and present innovative and creative product solutions. Requirements: Age is between 25 – 35 years oldBachelors degree in business, marketing, public relations, food scienceTwo to five years experience in marketing/product development and or Consumer Products marketingExperience in the fresh-cut industry strongly preferredExperience managing an agency or an outside resource a plusStrong computer literacy:  must be proficient in Word, Excel and PowerPointExcellent communication skills (verbal and written)Demonstrated success in marketing, requiring experience leading customer and senior management presentationsAdvanced spreadsheet and numerical analysis skills: business cases and margin analysisAttention to details and able to exercise tact and good interpersonal skillsGroup facilitation skillsTime management skillsMulti-tasking and able to be pro-active with a sense of urgency
